Title: Eat, smile, drive and bike
DateModified: '2019-03-02'
DatePublished: '2019-03-02'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/eat-smile-drive-and-bike
SetInCountry: Slovenia
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: Katia  Nanni
AuthorCountry: Italy
Text: "While i looking for the best road, the best itinerary,... I decided to start,\
  \ nothing planned, I just got that was the best idea I should have.\n\nSo, no plan,\
  \ no hotel, no reservation; only me, my bike and my soul. I assure you, it was enough.\
  \ \n\nSlovenia is the river country but not only, is also the trail country, full\
  \ of passionate and smiling people, most of them speak also Italian and I don\u2019\
  t lie when I said you that I really paid few stuff in a month, my smile was magical\
  \ appreciate in that country.. nobody looking for \u201Cextra\u201D, just me, my\
  \ smile, my story and my travel adventures.. best days of my life until now."
